sources.title: You're Not Alone | Full Movie | Mystery Horror | Katia Winter | Halloween 2022
sources.description:
You're Not Alone - After the premature death of her estranged husband, Emma (Winter) regains custody of their young daughter Isla (Jones) and hopes to rebuild their relationship after many years apart. But when an evil entity begins to torment them, mother and daughter are forced to face the inexplicable presence that inhabits the walls of their new home.
2020.  Stars: Katia Winter, Leya Catlett, Zach Avery

metadata.Plot: A Short mental health awareness film, focusing on a young teenage girl who has recently lost her dad. She struggles to cope at home with her mum and she slowly gives up. She gets visions of her dad but she isn't sure is that him. ...
